00:20:59,480 --> 00:21:01,900
 to je bilo baš znanstveni rad praktički.

754
00:21:02,900 --> 00:21:03,800
 I u tom radu,

755
00:21:03,800 --> 00:21:05,580
 kako sam na početku već rekla,

756
00:21:05,580 --> 00:21:06,700
 Lika mi je bila,

757
00:21:06,700 --> 00:21:08,920
 budući da je ona mučenješkog smrća umrla,

758
00:21:08,920 --> 00:21:10,500
 stiriljena je bila u Gospiču.

759
00:21:10,500 --> 00:21:12,360
 Onda sam se dosta bavila,

760
00:21:12,360 --> 00:21:14,120
 evo, i tim područjima,

761
00:21:14,120 --> 00:21:15,180
 različitim drugim područjima,

762
00:21:15,180 --> 00:21:16,660
 koji su vezani uz njezino djelovanje.

763
00:21:16,660 --> 00:21:18,480
 I od tog vremena,

764
00:21:18,480 --> 00:21:18,820
 znači,

765
00:21:18,820 --> 00:21:20,820
 to je možda prošlo deset godina,

766
00:21:20,820 --> 00:21:22,340
 njega je izišla i tako dalje,

767
00:21:22,340 --> 00:21:23,420
 onda sam upisala sam,

768
00:21:23,420 --> 00:21:24,900
 poslije diplomski studij,

769
00:21:24,900 --> 00:21:26,700
 i nastavila sam,

770
00:21:26,700 --> 00:21:27,940
 proširila sam tu temu

771
00:21:27,940 --> 00:21:29,120
 na svoju družbu,

772
00:21:29,120 --> 00:21:31,020
 znači, na, ubiti, kontekst cijeli,

773
00:21:31,020 --> 00:21:32,120
 znači, progoni družbe

774
00:21:32,120 --> 00:21:34,460
 od 1945. godine do 1952.

775
00:21:34,460 --> 00:21:35,040
 U postu kalisnička.

776
00:21:35,040 --> 00:21:36,160
 Opisali iz ti knjigo, je li tako?

777
00:21:36,160 --> 00:21:37,880
 Odnos Jugoslavijansko-komuničkog režima

778
00:21:37,880 --> 00:21:38,620
 prema družbi.

779
00:21:38,620 --> 00:21:41,180
 Tako je, to je Milo Serđa odkupljio i odmržio.

780
00:21:41,180 --> 00:21:41,860
 Baš sam htio pitati,

781
00:21:41,860 --> 00:21:43,060
 zašto te, zašto konkretno

782
00:21:43,060 --> 00:21:44,200
 od 1945. do 1952.

783
00:21:44,200 --> 00:21:45,740
 Zato što je to bilo porače

784
00:21:45,740 --> 00:21:46,940
 i to je bilo najintenzivnije,

785
00:21:47,060 --> 00:21:48,460
 razdoblje najintenzivnijih progona

786
00:21:48,460 --> 00:21:51,120
 ovdje, tako da u tom razdoblju

787
00:21:51,120 --> 00:21:52,080
 su stradale, mislim,

788
00:21:52,080 --> 00:21:54,160
 to je bilo represija na različitim,

789
00:21:54,160 --> 00:21:55,560
 evo, prvenstveno, to su ljudi

790
00:21:55,560 --> 00:21:56,520
 koji su bili osuđeni,

791
00:21:56,520 --> 00:21:57,440
 koji su bili ubijeni,

792
00:21:57,440 --> 00:21:59,580
 sestre, odnosno i članovi,

793
00:21:59,580 --> 00:22:00,760
 naravno, katoličke crkve,

794
00:22:00,760 --> 00:22:03,220
 ali postoje i drugi različiti načine

795
00:22:03,220 --> 00:22:04,600
 i provođenje represije nad...

796
00:22:04,600 --> 00:22:05,680
 Možete li precizirati,

797
00:22:05,680 --> 00:22:06,360
 ono malo navišt,

798
00:22:06,360 --> 00:22:07,400
 šta se to zapravo događalo

799
00:22:07,400 --> 00:22:08,380
 sa družbom za vreme

800
00:22:08,380 --> 00:22:09,720
 Jugoslavijanskog režima

801
00:22:09,720 --> 00:22:11,220
 od 45. do 50. i druge?

802
00:22:11,220 --> 00:22:13,080
 Pa, budući da je družba

803
00:22:13,080 --> 00:22:14,920
 bila najbrojnija u razdoblju,

804
00:22:14,920 --> 00:22:15,960
 znači, od kada je došla,

805
00:22:15,960 --> 00:22:17,780
 pa, evo, to je možda od 39. godine,

806
00:22:17,780 --> 00:22:20,180
 gledam drugi svjetski rat porače,

807
00:22:20,180 --> 00:22:22,760
 znači, najbrojnija ženska redovniška družba

808
00:22:22,760 --> 00:22:24,760
 zajednica na ovim prostorima,

809
00:22:24,760 --> 00:22:26,300
 tako da je to bilo jako...

810
00:22:26,300 --> 00:22:29,460
 evo, njihova naša djelatnost

811
00:22:29,460 --> 00:22:31,140
 je bila izuzetno razgranata,

812
00:22:31,140 --> 00:22:32,700
 to znate, velike škole,

813
00:22:32,700 --> 00:22:34,220
 bolnice i tako dalje,

814
00:22:34,220 --> 00:22:37,020
 i ono što se dogodilo je zaista,

815
00:22:37,020 --> 00:22:38,340
 znači, mislim,

816
00:22:38,520 --> 00:22:40,900
 katolička crkva kao neprijatelj države

817
00:22:40,900 --> 00:22:43,480
 nakon 45. godine

818
00:22:43,480 --> 00:22:44,940
 doživila velike progone

819
00:22:44,940 --> 00:22:46,860
 i bilo je potrebno obezvrijediti

820
00:22:46,860 --> 00:22:49,180
 ljude, znači, članove,

821
00:22:49,180 --> 00:22:50,340
 odnosno vjernike,

822
00:22:50,340 --> 00:22:51,700
 a, s druge strane,

823
00:22:51,700 --> 00:22:52,940
 oduzeti i ono što ima,

824
00:22:52,940 --> 00:22:54,040
 znači, materialnu imovinu,

825
00:22:54,040 --> 00:22:56,100
 tako da na ta dva područja

826
00:22:56,100 --> 00:22:58,340
 su se događale različite vrste represije,

827
00:22:58,340 --> 00:22:59,160
 to su...

828
00:22:59,160 --> 00:22:59,380
 Na primjer?

829
00:22:59,380 --> 00:23:01,540
 Na primjer, evo, idemo oduzimanje imovine,

830
00:23:01,540 --> 00:23:02,800
 to su škola i tako dalje,

831
00:23:02,800 --> 00:23:04,760
 nacionalizacija imovine,

832
00:23:04,760 --> 00:23:06,980
 konficiranje imovine i tako dalje,

833
00:23:07,320 --> 00:23:08,320
 a, s druge strane,

834
00:23:08,320 --> 00:23:10,040
 bile su lažne optužbe,

835
00:23:10,040 --> 00:23:12,040
 lažne optužbe, znači,

836
00:23:12,040 --> 00:23:13,500
 degradacija družbe,

837
00:23:13,500 --> 00:23:14,720
 nije samo moje, naravno,

838
00:23:14,720 --> 00:23:15,580
 ali sad ću govoriti

839
00:23:15,580 --> 00:23:17,280
 o članicama svoje družbe,

840
00:23:17,280 --> 00:23:19,080
 degradacija

841
00:23:19,080 --> 00:23:22,000
 proizvodnjom različitih

842
00:23:22,000 --> 00:23:23,480
 lažnih optužbi,

843
00:23:23,480 --> 00:23:24,860
 javnim suđenjima,

844
00:23:24,860 --> 00:23:25,580
 strijeljanjima,

845
00:23:25,580 --> 00:23:26,360
 evo, kao to su,

846
00:23:26,360 --> 00:23:27,620
 dugotrajnim kaznama,

847
00:23:28,280 --> 00:23:28,940
 zbog čega,

848
00:23:28,940 --> 00:23:30,160
 zato što je u javnosti

849
00:23:30,160 --> 00:23:30,700
 se željelo

850
00:23:30,700 --> 00:23:32,860
 prikazati da crkva,

851
00:23:32,860 --> 00:23:33,560
 odnosno, evo,

852
00:23:33,560 --> 00:23:35,440
 jedna ženska redovnijska družba

853
00:23:35,440 --> 00:23:36,340
 je ona koja,

854
00:23:36,340 --> 00:23:38,220
 u kojoj se ne smije imati povjerenja

855
00:23:38,220 --> 00:23:39,440
 i ne može imati povjerenja,

856
00:23:39,440 --> 00:23:40,680
 jer čini puno, puno tih

857
00:23:40,680 --> 00:23:42,080
 različitih zločina

858
00:23:42,080 --> 00:23:42,920
 pod navodnicima,

859
00:23:42,920 --> 00:23:43,320
 naravno,

860
00:23:43,320 --> 00:23:45,220
 tako da, evo,

861
00:23:45,220 --> 00:23:46,060
 to se ono događalo,

862
00:23:46,060 --> 00:23:47,900
 baš jedna velika medijska kampanja

863
00:23:47,900 --> 00:23:49,600
 protiv članica,

864
00:23:49,600 --> 00:23:51,260
 odnosno protiv katoličke crkve,

865
00:23:51,260 --> 00:23:52,160
 kao takve,

866
00:23:52,220 --> 00:23:53,100
 tako da, to je bilo i onda,

867
00:23:53,100 --> 00:23:54,540
 s druge strane,

868
00:23:54,540 --> 00:23:55,440
 ukloniti,

869
00:23:55,440 --> 00:23:58,020
 učiniti nevidljivim,

870
00:23:58,020 --> 00:23:59,320
 znači, nismo smijele nositi

871
00:23:59,320 --> 00:24:00,920
 redovnička u dijelu,

872
00:24:00,920 --> 00:24:02,800
 tako da su morale sestre raditi

873
00:24:02,800 --> 00:24:03,660
 gdje godi su bile,

874
00:24:03,660 --> 00:24:04,760
 znači, u civilu,

875
00:24:04,760 --> 00:24:05,140
 tako je,

876
00:24:05,140 --> 00:24:07,100
 osim škole,

877
00:24:07,100 --> 00:24:08,080
 znači, više nismo bilo,

878
00:24:08,080 --> 00:24:09,120
 postoje mogućnost

879
00:24:09,120 --> 00:24:10,840
 da se radi u školama

880
00:24:10,840 --> 00:24:11,400
 i tako da,

881
00:24:11,400 --> 00:24:11,820
 evo,

882
00:24:11,820 --> 00:24:12,760
 taj puno toga,

883
00:24:12,760 --> 00:24:13,380
 znači, ukloni,

884
00:24:13,380 --> 00:24:15,680
 učini nevidljivim

885
00:24:15,680 --> 00:24:17,420
 i obezvrijedi,

886
00:24:17,420 --> 00:24:19,500
 obezvrijedi s obzirom na,

887
00:24:19,500 --> 00:24:20,860
 evo, ukupno ono povjerenje

888
00:24:20,860 --> 00:24:21,860
 o kojem sam malo prije rekla,

889
00:24:21,860 --> 00:24:22,300
 znači, da,

890
00:24:22,300 --> 00:24:23,200
 to povjerenje

891
00:24:23,200 --> 00:24:24,640
 koje je narod,

892
00:24:24,640 --> 00:24:27,140
 koje imaju osobe,

893
00:24:27,140 --> 00:24:27,560
 znači,

894
00:24:27,560 --> 00:24:29,060
 naši sugrađani,

895
00:24:29,060 --> 00:24:30,540
 bilo ko u nas kao crkvu,

896
00:24:30,540 --> 00:24:31,380
 u nas kao redovnice,

897
00:24:31,380 --> 00:24:32,540
 to je nešto što je trebalo

898
00:24:32,540 --> 00:24:33,640
 obezvrijediti, da.

899
00:24:33,640 --> 00:24:34,820
 Koliko su članica,

900
00:24:34,820 --> 00:24:35,560
 koliko su članica

901
00:24:35,560 --> 00:24:36,500
 družba izgubila

902
00:24:36,500 --> 00:24:37,440
 u tom razdubju?

903
00:24:37,440 --> 00:24:38,200
 U tom razdubju,

904
00:24:38,200 --> 00:24:38,520
 znači,

905
00:24:38,520 --> 00:24:39,280
 bilo ih je,

906
00:24:39,280 --> 00:24:40,400
 evo, šest,

907
00:24:40,400 --> 00:24:41,720
 na području Hrvatske,

908
00:24:41,800 --> 00:24:42,860
 znači, šest mučenica,

909
00:24:42,860 --> 00:24:45,280
 stradale su također

910
00:24:45,280 --> 00:24:46,480
 sestre i,

911
00:24:46,480 --> 00:24:47,320
 dobro, kao,

912
00:24:47,320 --> 00:24:48,520
 evo, reklam mi se,

913
00:24:48,520 --> 00:24:49,740
 žrtve različitih napada

914
00:24:49,740 --> 00:24:50,400
 i tako dalje.

915
00:24:50,400 --> 00:24:52,940
 Preko 90-ih je bilo

916
00:24:52,940 --> 00:24:53,440
 osuđeno,

917
00:24:53,440 --> 00:24:53,960
 područje,

918
00:24:53,960 --> 00:24:54,280
 to je,

919
00:24:54,280 --> 00:24:56,640
 na dulje ili kraće,

920
00:24:56,640 --> 00:24:56,920
 znači,

921
00:24:56,920 --> 00:24:58,460
 trpilo je različite sudske

922
00:24:58,460 --> 00:24:59,120
 progone na,

923
00:24:59,120 --> 00:25:00,240
 i u Bosni i Hercegovini,

924
00:25:00,240 --> 00:25:01,260
 to je bilo i Slovenija,

925
00:25:01,260 --> 00:25:02,600
 Srbija i Hrvatska,

926
00:25:02,600 --> 00:25:02,920
 tako da,

927
00:25:02,920 --> 00:25:03,380
 puno je to,

928
00:25:03,380 --> 00:25:04,380
 buduće nas je bilo puno,

929
00:25:04,440 --> 00:25:05,560
 to se jako puno,

930
00:25:05,560 --> 00:25:05,780
 znači,

931
00:25:05,780 --> 00:25:06,060
 to je,

932
00:25:06,060 --> 00:25:06,940
 princip je bio,

933
00:25:06,940 --> 00:25:08,620
 imate velike bolnice,

934
00:25:08,620 --> 00:25:10,960
 u bolnicama zajednice se stara

935
00:25:10,960 --> 00:25:11,780
 koje su djelovale

936
00:25:11,780 --> 00:25:12,840
 i tu je bilo najlakše,

937
00:25:12,840 --> 00:25:14,420
 u biti je zdravstvo je najviše stradalo,

938
00:25:14,420 --> 00:25:15,360
 s obzirom na,

939
00:25:15,360 --> 00:25:16,560
 na ote lažne optužbe,

940
00:25:16,560 --> 00:25:18,160
 jer su bilo je najlakše,

941
00:25:18,160 --> 00:25:18,680
 znači,

942
00:25:18,680 --> 00:25:19,640
 neku,

943
00:25:19,640 --> 00:25:19,960
 evo,

944
00:25:19,960 --> 00:25:20,420
 optužbu,

945
00:25:20,420 --> 00:25:20,680
 znači,

946
00:25:20,680 --> 00:25:21,960
 ti si pomogao neprijatelju,

947
00:25:21,960 --> 00:25:22,420
 ti si mu,

948
00:25:22,420 --> 00:25:23,940
 ti si ustašamo donijela,

949
00:25:23,940 --> 00:25:25,160
 ne znam,

950
00:25:25,160 --> 00:25:25,460
 ja šta,

951
00:25:25,460 --> 00:25:26,740
 pomogla si neprijatelju

952
00:25:26,740 --> 00:25:27,820
 i temljen toga si,

953
00:25:28,000 --> 00:25:29,360
 donijela lijek ili bilo što,

954
00:25:29,360 --> 00:25:30,840
 to onda tako to bilo,

955
00:25:30,840 --> 00:25:31,060
 znači,

956
00:25:31,060 --> 00:25:31,960
 skupine se stara

957
00:25:31,960 --> 00:25:33,320
 koje su bile optužene

958
00:25:33,320 --> 00:25:34,000
 u jednom trenutku,

959
00:25:34,000 --> 00:25:34,240
 znači,

960
00:25:34,240 --> 00:25:34,480
 ne znam,

961
00:25:34,480 --> 00:25:35,680
 po deset njih,

962
00:25:35,680 --> 00:25:36,080
 tako da,

963
00:25:36,080 --> 00:25:37,560
 to je bilo baš jedno,

964
00:25:37,560 --> 00:25:39,040
 teško razdoblje gdje se,

965
00:25:39,040 --> 00:25:39,340
 evo,

966
00:25:39,340 --> 00:25:40,320
 opet su se isprofilirali,

967
00:25:40,320 --> 00:25:40,920
 ono što smo rekli,

968
00:25:40,920 --> 00:25:41,140
 znači,

969
00:25:41,140 --> 00:25:41,880
 kad imate put,

970
00:25:41,880 --> 00:25:44,420
 kad imaš to usmjerenje

971
00:25:44,420 --> 00:25:46,160
 i kad želiš odgovoriti

972
00:25:46,160 --> 00:25:46,900
 na Boži poziv

973
00:25:46,900 --> 00:25:47,420
 u tom trenutku

974
00:25:47,420 --> 00:25:47,920
 kad jesi,

975
00:25:47,920 --> 00:25:49,020
 to onda opet donosi

976
00:25:49,020 --> 00:25:49,800
 puno blagoslova,

977
00:25:49,860 --> 00:25:51,540
 ali svakako znate,

978
00:25:51,540 --> 00:25:53,140
 nije svatko jak

979
00:25:53,140 --> 00:25:54,640
 na jesni jednak način

980
00:25:54,640 --> 00:25:55,380
 i treba nekome

981
00:25:55,380 --> 00:25:56,860
 i puno vremena

982
00:25:56,860 --> 00:25:59,020
 da nekako prođe

983
00:25:59,020 --> 00:26:00,300
 kroz tu težinu

984
00:26:00,300 --> 00:26:02,880
 i nije svatko bio jak,

985
00:26:02,880 --> 00:26:03,140
 evo,

986
00:26:03,140 --> 00:26:03,640
 tako reki.

987
00:26:03,640 --> 00:26:06,180
 Ali ovih šeste stara

988
00:26:06,180 --> 00:26:06,860
 što ste nadjeli,

989
00:26:06,860 --> 00:26:07,940
 što su mučenice,

990
00:26:07,940 --> 00:26:08,600
 što ste rekli,

991
00:26:08,600 --> 00:26:10,480
 za njih se one su pokazale

992
00:26:10,480 --> 00:26:11,900
 po priličnom snagu,

993
00:26:11,900 --> 00:26:14,020
 time što su,

994
00:26:14,020 --> 00:26:14,300
 mislim,

995
00:26:14,300 --> 00:26:16,120
 ubijene su izmržnje prema vjeri,

996
00:26:16,120 --> 00:26:18,040
 i za njih se sada vodi

997
00:26:18,040 --> 00:26:19,500
 proces za sve njih,

998
00:26:19,700 --> 00:26:21,080
 za proglašenje blaženima,

999
00:26:21,080 --> 00:26:21,700
 tako je, da.

1000
00:26:21,700 --> 00:26:23,440
 A posebno se među njima,

1001
00:26:23,440 --> 00:26:25,320
 i stiče sestra Žarka i Vasić,

1002
00:26:25,320 --> 00:26:25,600
 pa evo,

1003
00:26:25,600 --> 00:26:27,160
 ako možete ono pari riječi,

1004
00:26:27,160 --> 00:26:28,140
 jednostavno njima,

1005
00:26:28,140 --> 00:26:29,020
 o sestri Žarki

1006
00:26:29,020 --> 00:26:29,940
 i o ostalim sestrama

1007
00:26:29,940 --> 00:26:31,340
 i o tom procesu

1008
00:26:31,340 --> 00:26:32,640
 gdje se on zapravo sada nalazi,

1009
00:26:32,640 --> 00:26:34,200
 on je pokrenut prije koliko godina?

1010
00:26:34,200 --> 00:26:39,160
 Ne znam, čekaj,

1011
00:26:39,160 --> 00:26:39,900
 od 2018.

1012
00:26:39,900 --> 00:26:41,180
 Od prvike.

1013
00:26:41,180 --> 00:26:43,980
 Jeste mislim da je 2018.

1014
00:26:43,980 --> 00:26:45,280
 Da, da sam čitao da je pisao.

1015
00:26:45,280 --> 00:26:47,020
 Dobro, ali eto,

1016
00:26:47,020 --> 00:26:48,180
 imamo što je da,

1017
00:26:48,740 --> 00:26:50,340
 s obzirom da

1018
00:26:50,340 --> 00:26:51,720
 nismo dovoljno upoznati

1019
00:26:51,720 --> 00:26:52,500
 sa svim tim stvarima

1020
00:26:52,500 --> 00:26:53,960
 koje su se događale

1021
00:26:53,960 --> 00:26:55,580
 u tom poratnom razdoblju

1022
00:26:55,580 --> 00:26:56,860
 i o mnogima se i nije smjelo

1023
00:26:56,860 --> 00:26:57,680
 iti razgovarati.

1024
00:26:57,680 --> 00:26:58,560
 Pa evo,

1025
00:26:58,560 --> 00:27:00,620
 pa čisto ono da malo sad

1026
00:27:00,620 --> 00:27:02,160
 svjetlo usmjerimo

1027
00:27:02,160 --> 00:27:02,980
 na one koji su dali

1028
00:27:02,980 --> 00:27:03,880
 svoj život za vjeru.

1029
00:27:04,280 --> 00:27:05,820
 eto, ako možete na malo riječi,

1030
00:27:05,820 --> 00:27:07,460
 par informacija o njima

1031
00:27:07,460 --> 00:27:08,680
 i učeniti o tom procesu.

1032
00:27:08,680 --> 00:27:09,420
 Da li napreduje,

1033
00:27:09,420 --> 00:27:10,400
 stojali na mjestu.

1034
00:27:10,400 --> 00:27:11,940
 Vi studijelite vnuter,

1035
00:27:11,940 --> 00:27:12,300
 ali tako?

1036
00:27:12,300 --> 00:27:13,640
 Znaš, ja sam malo izišla

1037
00:27:13,640 --> 00:27:14,000
 iz toga,

1038
00:27:14,000 --> 00:27:15,860
 nemojme baš toliko prozivati,

1039
00:27:15,860 --> 00:27:16,560
 sad su drugi ljudi,

1040
00:27:16,560 --> 00:27:17,300
 ja ti deset godina

1041
00:27:17,300 --> 00:27:18,080
 nisam u tim,

1042
00:27:18,080 --> 00:27:18,460
 znaš,

1043
00:27:18,460 --> 00:27:18,840
 vodama.

1044
00:27:19,560 --> 00:27:20,380
 Okej, ajmo mi sad

1045
00:27:20,380 --> 00:27:21,240
 na sestru Žarku.

1046
00:27:21,240 --> 00:27:24,520
 Kad god prišljam o njoj,

1047
00:27:24,520 --> 00:27:26,820
 uvijek, evo,

1048
00:27:26,820 --> 00:27:28,060
 možda ponovim ono,

1049
00:27:28,060 --> 00:27:29,920
 više ne znam točno

1050
00:27:29,920 --> 00:27:31,200
 što sam regla na početku,

1051
00:27:31,200 --> 00:27:34,120
 ali smatra me jednom

1052
00:27:34,120 --> 00:27:35,880
 od prekretnica u mom životu.

1053
00:27:35,880 --> 00:27:39,060
 Malo ću proširiti.

1054
00:27:39,060 --> 00:27:39,860
 Znači, kad god,

1055
00:27:39,860 --> 00:27:42,240
 kad god sam poslušala

1056
00:27:42,240 --> 00:27:44,880
 pozive,

1057
00:27:44,880 --> 00:27:45,740
 a to su bile moje,

1058
00:27:45,740 --> 00:27:46,820
 evo moje poglavarice,

1059
00:27:46,820 --> 00:27:48,040
 da nešto učini

1060
00:27:48,040 --> 00:27:49,480
 na području,

1061
00:27:49,560 --> 00:27:50,220
 karizme,

1062
00:27:50,220 --> 00:27:52,580
 to je uvijek ispalo

1063
00:27:52,580 --> 00:27:53,540
 jako dobro za mene

1064
00:27:53,540 --> 00:27:54,280
 i za moje zvanje.

1065
00:27:54,280 --> 00:27:56,380
 Tako, koda sam se učvršivala

1066
00:27:56,380 --> 00:27:56,920
 i ne koda,

1067
00:27:56,920 --> 00:27:58,120
 nego i jesam se učvršivala.

1068
00:27:58,120 --> 00:27:58,520
 Tako da,

1069
00:27:58,520 --> 00:28:00,320
 sestra Žarka

1070
00:28:00,320 --> 00:28:01,440
 mi je donijela

1071
00:28:01,440 --> 00:28:02,720
 jednu dodatnu

1072
00:28:02,720 --> 00:28:03,820
 životnu mudrost

1073
00:28:03,820 --> 00:28:05,520
 i osnažila me

1074
00:28:05,520 --> 00:28:06,820
 na puno područja

1075
00:28:06,820 --> 00:28:08,080
 moga osobnoga života.

1076
00:28:08,080 --> 00:28:09,520
 Jer sam nikad do tada

1077
00:28:09,520 --> 00:28:10,360
 nisam susrela,

1078
00:28:10,360 --> 00:28:11,200
 evo, sa tim,

1079
00:28:11,200 --> 00:28:12,140
 sa svjedocima,

1080
00:28:12,140 --> 00:28:13,040
 jer puno sam bila,

1081
00:28:13,040 --> 00:28:13,760
 evo, kako sam rekla,

1082
00:28:13,760 --> 00:28:14,340
 na terenu

1083
00:28:14,340 --> 00:28:15,900
 i razgovarala sam sa svjedocima

1084
00:28:15,900 --> 00:28:18,100
 koji su sestra Žarko poznavali,

1085
00:28:18,100 --> 00:28:19,600
 koji su sudjelovali

1086
00:28:19,600 --> 00:28:20,520
 možda u njezinom

1087
00:28:20,520 --> 00:28:22,760
 smaknuću,

1088
00:28:22,760 --> 00:28:24,800
 koji su s različitih strana,

1089
00:28:24,800 --> 00:28:25,900
 to je bilo jedan baš...

1090
00:28:25,900 --> 00:28:26,900
 Koji su udjelovali...

1091
00:28:26,900 --> 00:28:28,320
 U smaknuću,

1092
00:28:28,320 --> 00:28:29,280
 znači neko ko...

1093
00:28:29,280 --> 00:28:32,620
 Neću sad reći da oni koji su je ubili,

1094
00:28:32,620 --> 00:28:34,200
 ali koji su možda,

1095
00:28:34,200 --> 00:28:35,460
 evo, kao svjedoc,

1096
00:28:35,460 --> 00:28:36,460
 oni koji su vidjeli to,

1097
00:28:36,460 --> 00:28:38,260
 oni koji su vidjeli dokumente,

1098
00:28:38,260 --> 00:28:39,740
 koji su znali da će se to dogoditi,

1099
00:28:39,740 --> 00:28:40,440
 znači to sad,

1100
00:28:40,440 --> 00:28:42,140
 evo, da ne ispadne baš predramatično,

1101
00:28:42,140 --> 00:28:42,880
 nije to bilo to,

1102
00:28:42,880 --> 00:28:46,380
 ali uvijek sam tu donijela,

1103
00:28:46,380 --> 00:28:47,680
 dobila sam jednu dobru,

1104
00:28:47,680 --> 00:28:49,600
 jednu zaista važnost poznanju,

1105
00:28:49,600 --> 00:28:51,080
 što to znači uprostiti opraštanje

1106
00:28:51,080 --> 00:28:52,060
 i što čovjeku,

1107
00:28:52,060 --> 00:28:54,020
 što se čovjeku događa kad mrzi

1108
00:28:54,020 --> 00:28:56,120
 i da zaista ono možemo,

1109
00:28:56,120 --> 00:28:58,260
 tako jedna mržnja

1110
00:28:58,260 --> 00:28:59,180
 koja ti ostane,

1111
00:28:59,180 --> 00:29:03,500
 koliko destruktivno može,

1112
00:29:03,500 --> 00:29:05,560
 može, može, zaista rastočiti

1113
00:29:05,560 --> 00:29:08,380
 tvoj život cijelokupno,

1114
00:29:08,380 --> 00:29:09,640
 cijelinu tvojga života,

1115
00:29:09,640 --> 00:29:10,960
 evo, to možda taj dio

1116
00:29:10,960 --> 00:29:13,000
 i koliko ljudi koji pretrpe

1117
00:29:13,000 --> 00:29:15,520
 puno različitih i nepravdi,

1118
00:29:15,520 --> 00:29:16,240
 progonstva,

1119
00:29:16,240 --> 00:29:18,380
 svih težina životnih

1120
00:29:18,380 --> 00:29:19,980
 kad su u miru,

1121
00:29:19,980 --> 00:29:21,780
 kad su u tom,

1122
00:29:21,780 --> 00:29:23,240
 kad opraštaju

1123
00:29:23,240 --> 00:29:26,040
 i koliko to, bez obzira što je to težina

1124
00:29:26,040 --> 00:29:27,020
 koja je realno njih,

1125
00:29:27,400 --> 00:29:28,900
 evo, njihovo tijelo dotaknula

1126
00:29:28,900 --> 00:29:29,820
 kao nekakva sila

1127
00:29:29,820 --> 00:29:30,760
 koja je negativna,

1128
00:29:30,760 --> 00:29:31,200
 je li tako,

1129
00:29:31,200 --> 00:29:34,100
 to na njih jednostavno nema utjecaj,

1130
00:29:34,100 --> 00:29:35,780
 nego je nešto potpuno drugačije,

1131
00:29:35,780 --> 00:29:36,680
 to im donese blagost.

1132
00:29:36,680 --> 00:29:37,120
 Tako da,

1133
00:29:37,120 --> 00:29:39,020
 taj razlika između upraštanja

1134
00:29:39,020 --> 00:29:40,100
 i mržnje,

1135
00:29:40,100 --> 00:29:41,800
 to me je bilo jako jasno.

1136
00:29:42,200 --> 00:29:43,460
 nisam dotaknula sestru Žarko,

1137
00:29:43,460 --> 00:29:43,860
 znači,

1138
00:29:43,860 --> 00:29:46,180
 ona je bila medicinska sestra,

1139
00:29:46,180 --> 00:29:47,760
 ona je bila polničarka

1140
00:29:47,760 --> 00:29:49,540
 i bila je osuđena

1141
00:29:49,540 --> 00:29:51,760
 zbog toga što je na koncu pomagala

1142
00:29:51,760 --> 00:29:52,260
 siromasima,

1143
00:29:52,260 --> 00:29:53,320
 pomagala je svakom čovjeku

1144
00:29:53,320 --> 00:29:53,880
 bez razlike

1145
00:29:53,880 --> 00:29:54,680
 i partizanima,

1146
00:29:54,680 --> 00:29:55,200
 i ustašama,

1147
00:29:55,200 --> 00:29:55,540
 i ovima,

1148
00:29:55,540 --> 00:29:55,880
 i onima.

1149
00:29:55,880 --> 00:29:56,460
 Znači,

1150
00:29:56,460 --> 00:29:56,900
 ona je to,

1151
00:29:56,900 --> 00:29:58,780
 taj njezin životni odabir

1152
00:29:58,780 --> 00:29:59,900
 je bio iskoristen,

1153
00:29:59,900 --> 00:30:01,100
 kao što sam malo prije rekla,

1154
00:30:01,100 --> 00:30:02,800
 za nepravednu osudu.

1155
00:30:02,880 --> 00:30:03,380
 još k tome,

1156
00:30:03,380 --> 00:30:04,320
 bila je iz Krašića

1157
00:30:04,320 --> 00:30:06,220
 i to je dodalo njezinoj optužbi

1158
00:30:06,220 --> 00:30:07,520
 još jedan dodatan,

1159
00:30:07,520 --> 00:30:07,900
 evo,

1160
00:30:07,900 --> 00:30:08,840
 taj medijski,

1161
00:30:08,840 --> 00:30:09,720
 odnosno,

1162
00:30:09,720 --> 00:30:12,340
 taj jednu dimenziju

1163
00:30:12,340 --> 00:30:13,700
 koja je jednostavno išla prema tome

1164
00:30:13,700 --> 00:30:14,800
 da se degradira

1165
00:30:14,800 --> 00:30:15,640
 i, naravno,

1166
00:30:15,640 --> 00:30:16,480
 i kardinal Stepinas

1167
00:30:16,480 --> 00:30:17,620
 i da je to sve skupa nešto

1168
00:30:17,620 --> 00:30:19,220
 što je međusobno povezano,

1169
00:30:19,220 --> 00:30:20,040
 da je vezano sa,

1170
00:30:20,040 --> 00:30:21,100
 evo,

1171
00:30:21,100 --> 00:30:22,160
 zločinima protiv države,

1172
00:30:22,160 --> 00:30:23,280
 odnosno sa ustaštvu.

1173
00:30:23,280 --> 00:30:25,480
 Znači,

1174
00:30:25,480 --> 00:30:25,800
 ona je,

1175
00:30:25,800 --> 00:30:27,760
 radila je u Utočicu

1176
00:30:27,760 --> 00:30:28,740
 i tamo se dogodio

1177
00:30:28,740 --> 00:30:29,560
 određeni zločin

1178
00:30:29,560 --> 00:30:31,080
 za koju je ona poslije bila

1179
00:30:31,080 --> 00:30:32,300
 optužena

1180
00:30:32,300 --> 00:30:32,980
 poslije rata

1181
00:30:32,980 --> 00:30:35,140
 i ono što je za nju

1182
00:30:35,140 --> 00:30:35,800
 bilo baš,

1183
00:30:35,800 --> 00:30:36,140
 evo,

1184
00:30:36,140 --> 00:30:38,420
 važno je taj možda njezin put,

1185
00:30:38,420 --> 00:30:39,900
 kako sam sada

1186
00:30:39,900 --> 00:30:40,820
 rekla sa vam prije,

1187
00:30:40,820 --> 00:30:41,640
 nego ćemo se susreti,

1188
00:30:41,640 --> 00:30:42,240
 da imamo jednu,

1189
00:30:42,240 --> 00:30:43,440
 njede polima kuću

1190
00:30:43,440 --> 00:30:44,240
 blizu Gospića

1191
00:30:44,240 --> 00:30:45,080
 i sad svake put kad

1192
00:30:45,080 --> 00:30:45,960
 idem tamo

1193
00:30:45,960 --> 00:30:46,320
 i dosta

1194
00:30:46,320 --> 00:30:47,900
 i kod,

1195
00:30:47,900 --> 00:30:48,960
 kod ovoga,

1196
00:30:48,960 --> 00:30:50,100
 Gospičkog zatvora

1197
00:30:50,100 --> 00:30:50,400
 radim,

1198
00:30:50,400 --> 00:30:52,480
 imamo i određene usluge

1199
00:30:52,480 --> 00:30:53,400
 u Gospičkom zatvoru

1200
00:30:53,400 --> 00:30:54,140
 i uviste sjetim nje

1201
00:30:54,140 --> 00:30:56,540
 i taj možda njezin put

1202
00:30:56,540 --> 00:30:57,880
 i ono što je ona proživljavala

1203
00:30:57,880 --> 00:30:59,240
 u Gospičkom zatvoru,

1204
00:30:59,240 --> 00:31:00,220
 to je jedno razdoblje

1205
00:31:00,220 --> 00:31:01,840
