1208
00:31:05,420 --> 00:31:06,580
 i na koncu

1209
00:31:06,580 --> 00:31:08,100
 grad Gospić

1210
00:31:08,100 --> 00:31:09,220
 i stanovnici

1211
00:31:09,220 --> 00:31:10,440
 su nju prihvatili

1212
00:31:10,440 --> 00:31:11,500
 čak prije nego mi

1213
00:31:11,500 --> 00:31:12,760
 kao svoju mučenicu,

1214
00:31:12,760 --> 00:31:14,040
 kao čuvaricu nečega

1215
00:31:14,040 --> 00:31:14,600
 vrijednoga,

1216
00:31:14,600 --> 00:31:15,540
 znači čuvaricu

1217
00:31:15,540 --> 00:31:16,840
 poklada vjere,

1218
00:31:16,840 --> 00:31:18,540
 čuvaricu domovinskog

1219
00:31:18,540 --> 00:31:19,740
 jednoga nečega

1220
00:31:19,740 --> 00:31:21,560
 što je domovinskog identiteta,

1221
00:31:21,720 --> 00:31:22,340
 tako da

1222
00:31:22,340 --> 00:31:23,660
 ona nakon svoje smrti

1223
00:31:23,660 --> 00:31:24,640
 na Gospičkom groblju

1224
00:31:24,640 --> 00:31:25,300
 je ostala,

1225
00:31:25,300 --> 00:31:26,480
 ostala je tamo,

1226
00:31:26,480 --> 00:31:26,740
