1227
00:31:26,740 --> 00:31:27,600
 i mi smo,

1228
00:31:27,600 --> 00:31:29,240
 nama je trebao neko vrijeme

1229
00:31:29,240 --> 00:31:29,720
 da se mi,

1230
00:31:29,720 --> 00:31:31,320
 da mi dođemo do nje,

1231
00:31:31,320 --> 00:31:32,260
 iako smo je nosili

1232
00:31:32,260 --> 00:31:33,600
 kao žrtvu,

1233
00:31:33,600 --> 00:31:35,520
 kao svoju susestru

1234
00:31:35,520 --> 00:31:36,440
 koja je bila uvijena

1235
00:31:36,440 --> 00:31:37,040
 baš zbog vjera,

1236
00:31:37,040 --> 00:31:37,700
 ali je isto tako

1237
00:31:37,700 --> 00:31:38,660
 trebalo nama vremena

1238
00:31:38,660 --> 00:31:40,020
 da dođemo do nje,

1239
00:31:40,020 --> 00:31:40,840
 baš fizički,

1240
00:31:40,840 --> 00:31:41,280
 jednostavno,

1241
00:31:41,280 --> 00:31:42,680
 da jednostavno dođemo

1242
00:31:42,680 --> 00:31:43,280
 do tog groba

1243
00:31:43,280 --> 00:31:45,240
 i da se počne odvijati

1244
00:31:45,240 --> 00:31:45,900
 taj proces

1245
00:31:45,900 --> 00:31:48,100
 vrednovanja

1246
00:31:48,100 --> 00:31:48,960
 svega toga

1247
00:31:48,960 --> 00:31:49,760
 što se dogodilo,

1248
00:31:49,760 --> 00:31:51,240
 vrednovanja tog trenutka

1249
00:31:51,240 --> 00:31:51,900
 povijesti

1250
00:31:51,900 --> 00:31:53,260
 i taj njezine žrtve

1251
00:31:53,260 --> 00:31:53,900
 koja je bila,

1252
00:31:53,900 --> 00:31:54,880
 evo takva da,

1253
00:31:54,880 --> 00:31:56,420
 da nakon su završila

1254
00:31:56,420 --> 00:31:58,300
 i mučeneškom svrću.

1255
00:31:58,300 --> 00:31:59,900
 Spomenuli ste

1256
00:31:59,900 --> 00:32:00,620
 Depol,

1257
00:32:00,620 --> 00:32:01,860
 pa sad ono možemo

1258
00:32:01,860 --> 00:32:03,400
 preći na glavnu temu

1259
00:32:03,400 --> 00:32:03,800
 ovog

1260
00:32:03,800 --> 00:32:04,640
 našeg

1261
00:32:04,640 --> 00:32:06,340
 razgovora.

1262
00:32:07,440 --> 00:32:08,660
 vi ste

1263
00:32:08,660 --> 00:32:09,820
 direktorica

1264
00:32:09,820 --> 00:32:10,660
 Depol Hrvatske.

1265
00:32:10,660 --> 00:32:11,360
 Tako,

1266
00:32:11,360 --> 00:32:11,900
 predsjednica

1267
00:32:11,900 --> 00:32:12,240
 odruge.

1268
00:32:12,240 --> 00:32:13,020
 Predsjednica odruge.

1269
00:32:13,020 --> 00:32:13,960
 Dobro,

1270
00:32:13,960 --> 00:32:14,280
 znači,

1271
00:32:14,280 --> 00:32:15,740
 postoji vaša družba

1272
00:32:15,740 --> 00:32:16,960
 i postoji

1273
00:32:16,960 --> 00:32:18,160
 Depol Hrvatska,

1274
