 da mi razdvojite

1278
00:32:21,120 --> 00:32:22,160
 te dvije stvarnosti

1279
00:32:22,160 --> 00:32:22,820
 o čemu se radi.

1280
00:32:22,820 --> 00:32:23,260
 Hoću.

1281
00:32:23,260 --> 00:32:24,100
 Idemo prvo

1282
00:32:24,100 --> 00:32:24,920
 ne na razvojanje

1283
00:32:24,920 --> 00:32:25,980
 nego na spajanje

1284
00:32:25,980 --> 00:32:27,740
 koje je

1285
00:32:27,740 --> 00:32:28,120
 u biti

1286
00:32:28,120 --> 00:32:28,400
 mi smo

1287
00:32:28,400 --> 00:32:29,300
 sestra milostanice

1288
00:32:29,300 --> 00:32:29,880
 Svetog Vinka

1289
00:32:29,880 --> 00:32:30,600
 Pauluskog.

1290
00:32:30,600 --> 00:32:31,680
 Je tao Pauluski

1291
00:32:31,680 --> 00:32:33,100
 je hrvatska

1292
00:32:33,100 --> 00:32:33,660
 inačica

1293
00:32:37,440 --> 00:32:38,240
 Saint Depol

1294
00:32:38,240 --> 00:32:39,720
 i taj Depol Hrvatska

1295
00:32:39,720 --> 00:32:40,180
 je, evo,

1296
00:32:40,180 --> 00:32:40,900
 taj francuski

1297
00:32:40,900 --> 00:32:41,480
 original,

1298
00:32:41,480 --> 00:32:41,820
 znači,

1299
00:32:41,820 --> 00:32:42,660
 on je to Vinka Pauluski.

1300
00:32:42,660 --> 00:32:43,460
 Povezuje nas

1301
00:32:43,460 --> 00:32:44,260
 Vinka Pauluski,

1302
00:32:44,260 --> 00:32:45,700
 povezuje nas

1303
00:32:45,700 --> 00:32:47,400
 ta karizma,

1304
00:32:47,400 --> 00:32:48,060
 služenja.

1305
00:32:48,060 --> 00:32:50,140
 Sad ovako,

1306
00:32:50,140 --> 00:32:51,620
 riječke

1307
00:32:51,620 --> 00:32:52,640
 sestre milostanice

1308
00:32:52,640 --> 00:32:53,920
 su od svog

1309
00:32:53,920 --> 00:32:54,960
 dolazka u rijeku

1310
00:32:54,960 --> 00:32:55,980
 uvijek bile usmjerene

1311
00:32:55,980 --> 00:32:56,780
 na beskućnike,

1312
00:32:56,780 --> 00:32:57,200
 znači,

1313
00:32:57,200 --> 00:32:57,940
 na najciromašnje

1314
00:32:57,940 --> 00:32:58,540
 od ciromašnjeg,

1315
00:32:58,540 --> 00:32:58,760
 znači,

1316
00:32:58,760 --> 00:32:59,420
 to je od sredine

1317
00:32:59,420 --> 00:33:00,400
 19. stoljeća,

1318
00:33:00,400 --> 00:33:01,320
 pa praktičke,

1319
00:33:01,320 --> 00:33:01,500
 evo,

1320
00:33:01,540 --> 00:33:08,140
 razvio na različite načine

1321
00:33:08,140 --> 00:33:10,200
 i u jednom trenutku,

1322
00:33:10,200 --> 00:33:11,580
 kako se povećao broj osoba

1323
00:33:11,580 --> 00:33:12,820
 koji su tražile pomoć,

1324
00:33:12,820 --> 00:33:13,700
 bili su beskućnice,

1325
00:33:13,700 --> 00:33:14,780
 mi smo izgradile kuću

1326
00:33:14,780 --> 00:33:16,140
 koja se zove Kuća Utočišta,

1327
00:33:16,140 --> 00:33:17,540
 to je 2007. godine

1328
00:33:17,540 --> 00:33:19,840
 i ta kuća je imala

1329
00:33:19,840 --> 00:33:21,420
 mogućnost prehrane,

1330
00:33:21,420 --> 00:33:22,060
 higijene

1331
00:33:22,060 --> 00:33:23,320
 i radila je,

1332
00:33:23,320 --> 00:33:23,560
 znači,

1333
00:33:23,560 --> 00:33:24,240
 mi smo same,

1334
00:33:24,240 --> 00:33:26,080
 same sestre su,

1335
00:33:26,080 --> 00:33:26,300
 znači,

1336
00:33:26,300 --> 00:33:27,220
 s pomoć volontera,

1337
00:33:27,220 --> 00:33:29,180
 vodile smo tu kuću

1338
00:33:29,180 --> 00:33:30,020
 i praktički,

1339
00:33:30,020 --> 00:33:30,240
 evo,

1340
00:33:30,240 --> 00:33:30,680
 te su se,

1341
00:33:30,680 --> 00:33:32,120
 razvijalo se to

1342
00:33:32,120 --> 00:33:33,120
 kroz jednih 10 godina,

1343
00:33:33,120 --> 00:33:33,800
 ali onda je sve to,

1344
00:33:33,800 --> 00:33:34,040
 znate,

1345
00:33:34,040 --> 00:33:35,080
 ono što smo rekli,

1346
00:33:35,080 --> 00:33:35,980
 taj kao poziv

1347
00:33:35,980 --> 00:33:36,880
 i kao naš život

1348
00:33:36,880 --> 00:33:38,220
 dođe vrijeme

1349
00:33:38,220 --> 00:33:39,400
 daljeg razvoja

1350
00:33:39,400 --> 00:33:40,700
 i sad to slušanje duha,

1351
00:33:40,700 --> 00:33:42,760
 odnosno otvaranje očiju

1352
00:33:42,760 --> 00:33:43,840
 za nove stvarnosti,

1353
00:33:43,840 --> 00:33:44,960
 nas, sestre,

1354
00:33:44,960 --> 00:33:45,320
 znači,

1355
00:33:45,320 --> 00:33:46,800
 je dovelo do toga

1356
00:33:46,800 --> 00:33:48,780
 da smo odlučili osnovati,

1357
00:33:48,780 --> 00:33:49,960
 evo jednu novu,

1358
00:33:49,960 --> 00:33:52,340
 to je udruga sada,

1359
00:33:52,340 --> 00:33:53,180
 ali jednostavno

1360
00:33:53,180 --> 00:33:53,900
 povezati se

1361
00:33:53,900 --> 00:33:55,300
 sa međunarodnom organizacijom

1362
00:33:55,300 --> 00:33:56,520
 koja je usmjerena

1363
00:33:59,180 --> 00:34:00,220
 bezkućnicima

1364
00:34:00,220 --> 00:34:01,000
 i djeluje,

1365
00:34:01,000 --> 00:34:02,660
 djeluje baš,

1366
00:34:02,660 --> 00:34:02,820
 evo,

1367
00:34:02,820 --> 00:34:03,460
 na tom području,

1368
00:34:03,460 --> 00:34:04,140
 kako sam rekla

1369
00:34:04,140 --> 00:34:05,600
 i to smo učinili,

1370
00:34:05,600 --> 00:34:06,260
 to je jedna

1371
00:34:06,260 --> 00:34:07,800
 međunarodni depol

1372
00:34:07,800 --> 00:34:09,680
 koji ima svoje sjedište

1373
00:34:09,680 --> 00:34:11,360
 u Londonu

1374
00:34:11,360 --> 00:34:12,440
 i nakon nekoliko godina,

1375
00:34:12,440 --> 00:34:12,740
 znači,

1376
00:34:12,740 --> 00:34:13,480
 to je možda gledamo

1377
00:34:13,480 --> 00:34:15,940
 od 2007.

1378
00:34:15,940 --> 00:34:17,980
 do 2017.

1379
00:34:17,980 --> 00:34:21,600
 i negdje oko 2015.

1380
00:34:21,600 --> 00:34:22,380
 smo počeli

1381
00:34:22,380 --> 00:34:23,260
 razgovarati,

1382
00:34:23,260 --> 00:34:23,540
 znači,

1383
00:34:23,540 --> 00:34:24,200
 ići u,

1384
00:34:24,200 --> 00:34:25,360
 jednostavno,

1385
00:34:25,360 --> 00:34:27,540
 međusobno se upoznavati

1386
00:34:27,540 --> 00:34:29,300
 i vidjeti možemo li zajedno

1387
00:34:29,300 --> 00:34:30,180
 ići dalje.

1388
00:34:30,180 --> 00:34:31,080
 Tako da,

1389
00:34:31,080 --> 00:34:32,600
 to je 2017.

1390
00:34:32,600 --> 00:34:33,600
 kada je

1391
00:34:33,600 --> 00:34:35,420
 kraj 2016.

1392
00:34:35,420 --> 00:34:36,400
 je osnovana udruga,

1393
00:34:36,400 --> 00:34:36,660
 znači,

1394
00:34:36,660 --> 00:34:37,980
 sljedeće godine smo 10 godina,

1395
00:34:37,980 --> 00:34:39,980
 udruga Depol Hrvatska

1396
00:34:39,980 --> 00:34:42,180
 i polako smo počeli se

1397
00:34:42,180 --> 00:34:43,340
 dalje razvijati.

1398
00:34:43,340 --> 00:34:45,360
 Kako su osnovne službe

1399
00:34:45,360 --> 00:34:46,900
 Depol Hrvatske,

1400
00:34:46,900 --> 00:34:48,080
 čime se on konkretno bavi,

1401
00:34:48,080 --> 00:34:48,960
 osim beskućnicima

1402
00:34:48,960 --> 00:34:49,880
 koje ste spomenuli,

1403
00:34:49,880 --> 00:34:51,220
 to je baš ono fuksirano

1404
00:34:51,220 --> 00:34:52,660
 isključivo na beskućnike

1405
00:34:52,660 --> 00:34:54,100
 ili imate još nekakve djelatnosti

1406
00:34:54,100 --> 00:34:54,780
 u sklopu Depola?

1407
00:34:54,780 --> 00:34:55,280
 Pa evo,

1408
00:34:55,400 --> 00:34:57,360
 beskućnici i osobe u riziku beskućništva,

1409
00:34:57,360 --> 00:34:59,260
 ali smo praktički registrirani,

1410
00:34:59,260 --> 00:35:00,320
 sve u toj kažemo za sebe

1411
00:35:00,320 --> 00:35:00,680
 da smo,

1412
00:35:00,680 --> 00:35:01,460
 možda i,

1413
00:35:01,460 --> 00:35:03,560
 mislim da jesmo jedina udruga u Hrvatskoj

1414
00:35:03,560 --> 00:35:04,180
 koja je registrirana

1415
00:35:04,180 --> 00:35:06,020
 isključivo samo za beskućnike.

1416
00:35:06,020 --> 00:35:06,320
 S time,

1417
00:35:06,320 --> 00:35:07,580
 kada gledamo,

1418
00:35:07,580 --> 00:35:07,840
 evo,

1419
00:35:07,840 --> 00:35:08,160
 to sam,

1420
00:35:08,160 --> 00:35:09,820
 proširila sam rizik beskućništva,

1421
00:35:09,820 --> 00:35:10,020
 evo,

1422
00:35:10,020 --> 00:35:10,400
 na primjer,

1423
00:35:10,400 --> 00:35:11,460
 to su osobe koje,

1424
00:35:11,460 --> 00:35:11,640
 evo,

1425
00:35:11,640 --> 00:35:13,520
 radimo sa zatvorenicima,

1426
00:35:13,520 --> 00:35:17,080
 koji nemaju praktički prebivališta,

1427
00:35:17,080 --> 00:35:18,380
 nemaju gdje ići

1428
00:35:18,380 --> 00:35:19,920
 nakon služenja svoje kazne,

1429
00:35:19,920 --> 00:35:20,480
 tako da radimo

1430
00:35:20,480 --> 00:35:21,300
 unutar zatvora

1431
00:35:21,300 --> 00:35:22,000
 i poslije toga.

1432
00:35:22,000 --> 00:35:22,620
 To je taj nekako,

1433
00:35:22,620 --> 00:35:23,760
 samo da govorim to,

1434
00:35:23,760 --> 00:35:25,060
 zbog razumijavanja što to znači

1435
00:35:25,060 --> 00:35:25,840
 rizik beskućnice.

1436
00:35:25,840 --> 00:35:27,800
 Znači osobe koje su,

1437
00:35:27,800 --> 00:35:31,080
 koje vrlo lako mogu postati beskućnici,

1438
00:35:31,080 --> 00:35:32,780
 ili zbog ovakve situacije

1439
00:35:32,780 --> 00:35:33,460
 koje sam navela,

1440
00:35:33,460 --> 00:35:35,220
 ili se na primjer nalaze

1441
00:35:35,220 --> 00:35:36,840
 u teškim financijskim situacijama,

1442
00:35:36,840 --> 00:35:38,380
 je to uvijek spominjem umjerovljenike,

1443
00:35:38,380 --> 00:35:40,500
 kada imaju puno,

1444
00:35:40,500 --> 00:35:42,600
 puno materijalnih troškova

1445
00:35:42,600 --> 00:35:45,240
 i jednostavno nisu u mogućnosti

1446
00:35:45,240 --> 00:35:46,460
 kroz određene razdoblje

1447
00:35:46,460 --> 00:35:48,080
 podmiriti te troškovi

1448
00:35:48,080 --> 00:35:49,340
 i to im spada isto tako,

1449
00:35:49,340 --> 00:35:51,060
 znači mogu sutra ostati bez stana,

1450
00:35:51,060 --> 00:35:52,320
 mogu ostati bez bilo čega

1451
00:35:52,320 --> 00:35:54,300
 i tako mi jednostavno ulječemo,

1452
00:35:54,300 --> 00:35:54,780
 reklo bi se,

1453
00:35:54,780 --> 00:35:56,140
 te neke praznine u sustavu

1454
00:35:56,140 --> 00:35:56,500
 koje,

1455
00:35:56,500 --> 00:35:59,040
 koje u biti bi mogla vrlo lako

1456
00:35:59,040 --> 00:36:01,180
 učiniti čovjeka beskućnikom.

1457
00:36:01,320 --> 00:36:03,460
 To je taj rizik samo da se razumije

1458
00:36:03,460 --> 00:36:04,980
 što to znači nama.

1459
00:36:04,980 --> 00:36:08,200
 I Depoli ima kuću utočišta u Rijeci,

1460
00:36:08,200 --> 00:36:11,020
 imate, spomenuli ste kuću u Gospiču.

1461
00:36:11,020 --> 00:36:12,540
 Kuću u blizu Gospiča.

1462
00:36:12,540 --> 00:36:13,240
 Blizu Gospiča.

1463
00:36:13,240 --> 00:36:15,240
 I imate još radite

1464
00:36:15,240 --> 00:36:16,780
 sa zatvorenicima u Gospiču

1465
00:36:16,780 --> 00:36:19,620
 i u Rijeci isto sa zatvorenicima.

1466
00:36:19,620 --> 00:36:20,320
 Da, da, tako je.

1467
00:36:20,320 --> 00:36:21,280
 Jako zanimljivo.

1468
00:36:21,280 --> 00:36:22,660
 Koliko otprilike imate korisnika,

1469
00:36:22,660 --> 00:36:23,940
 koliko korisnika prođe

1470
00:36:23,940 --> 00:36:25,380
 kroz Depola?

1471
00:36:25,380 --> 00:36:28,240
 Znaš je program više od 350 godišnje.

1472
00:36:28,240 --> 00:36:29,200
 To je to, znači,

1473
00:36:29,280 --> 00:36:30,260
 na različite načine.

1474
00:36:30,260 --> 00:36:32,280
 Netko će ići,

1475
00:36:32,280 --> 00:36:34,160
 neko će primiti uslugu prehrane,

1476
00:36:34,160 --> 00:36:34,860
 neko će uglavnom,

1477
00:36:34,860 --> 00:36:36,580
 ali to su na različite načine.

1478
00:36:36,580 --> 00:36:37,580
 Evo, pa što je taj broj.

1479
00:36:37,580 --> 00:36:38,540
 Znači, više od 350.

1480
00:36:38,540 --> 00:36:39,960
 A velik broj njih,

1481
00:36:39,960 --> 00:36:41,060
 kako sam shvatio,

1482
00:36:41,060 --> 00:36:43,080
 prima redovitu pomoć, zapravo.

1483
00:36:43,080 --> 00:36:44,520
 Na dnevnoj bazi.

1484
00:36:44,520 --> 00:36:45,420
 Da, da, tako je.

1485
00:36:45,420 --> 00:36:45,840
 Sigurno.

1486
00:36:45,840 --> 00:36:47,040
 Koliko imate korisnika

1487
00:36:47,040 --> 00:36:48,940
 kući i utočišta u rijeci dnevno, da?

1488
00:36:48,940 --> 00:36:50,480
 Dnevno, pa ja bih rekla

1489
00:36:50,480 --> 00:36:51,480
 maksimalno 70.

1490
00:36:51,480 --> 00:36:52,500
 To bi bilo to 70.

1491
00:36:52,500 --> 00:36:54,540
 I kako izgleda život u kući i utočišta?

1492
00:36:54,540 --> 00:36:57,020
 Pa, najbolji način...

1493
00:36:57,020 --> 00:36:58,340
 Ona nije tamo zaprespavati,

1494
00:36:58,340 --> 00:36:59,760
 ona je sad dnevni poravak

1495
00:36:59,760 --> 00:37:00,600
 bez kućnika.

1496
00:37:00,600 --> 00:37:02,040
 Tako je, mi imamo praktički,

1497
00:37:02,040 --> 00:37:04,100
 ja gledam, imamo sve što vama treba

1498
00:37:04,100 --> 00:37:05,640
 u vašoj kući, vašem domu,

1499
00:37:05,640 --> 00:37:08,020
 izuzev kreveta, odnosno izuzev spavalja.

1500
00:37:08,020 --> 00:37:09,860
 Ali dobro, imamo 12 sati sigurnosti,

1501
00:37:09,860 --> 00:37:12,820
 12 sati mogućnosti da čovjek bude kod nas

1502
00:37:12,820 --> 00:37:14,280
 i odspava barem preko dana,

1503
00:37:14,280 --> 00:37:15,580
 da beskućnik bude kod nas

1504
00:37:15,580 --> 00:37:16,640
 i pa odspava barem preko dana.

1505
00:37:16,640 --> 00:37:17,540
 To je puno.

1506
00:37:17,540 --> 00:37:19,480
 Znači, jedna utočište sigurnost

1507
00:37:19,480 --> 00:37:22,040
 u tih 12 sati, to je nešto što je stvarno,

1508
00:37:22,040 --> 00:37:24,100
 mislim da je to dosta važno njima svima.

1509
00:37:24,100 --> 00:37:25,500
 Ali više od toga,

1510
00:37:25,800 --> 00:37:28,420
 te činjenice da imamo kuću,

1511
00:37:28,420 --> 00:37:29,680
 da imamo jednu zgrađevinu,

1512
00:37:29,680 --> 00:37:31,900
 imamo osobe, znači to ima čovike,

1513
00:37:31,900 --> 00:37:33,860
 volonter, djelatnik,

1514
00:37:33,860 --> 00:37:37,000
 mi smo svi svaki dan za njih.

1515
00:37:37,000 --> 00:37:39,600
 I ta činjenica da možeš dostati otvorena vrata

1516
00:37:39,600 --> 00:37:40,660
 i da zaista možeš doći,

1517
00:37:40,660 --> 00:37:42,980
 da netko će biti tu za tebe.

1518
00:37:42,980 --> 00:37:44,980
 I to je, mislim da nekako...

1519
00:37:44,980 --> 00:37:46,300
 Netko će ponuditi hranu,

1520
00:37:46,300 --> 00:37:46,560
 netko će ponuditi...

1521
00:37:46,560 --> 00:37:47,840
 Netko će učiniti što god.

1522
00:37:47,840 --> 00:37:49,340
 Da imate i...

1523
00:37:49,340 --> 00:37:51,640
 Imamo duhovnu pomoć, psihološku pomoć,

1524
00:37:51,640 --> 00:37:53,020
 imamo higijeno, hranu,

1525
00:37:53,100 --> 00:37:55,340
 znači to su spada, mi to kažemo, temene usluge,

1526
00:37:55,340 --> 00:37:56,660
 hrana, higijena, zdravlje,

1527
00:37:56,660 --> 00:37:58,580
 onda imamo specializirane usluge,

1528
00:37:58,580 --> 00:38:00,160
 rad sa uvisnicima o alkoholu,

1529
00:38:00,160 --> 00:38:02,000
 zatvorenicima, bivših zatvorenicima,

1530
00:38:02,000 --> 00:38:05,340
 što je vašem društveno poduzetništvo,

1531
00:38:05,340 --> 00:38:08,240
 mogućnost radne aktivacije i zapošljavanja.

1532
00:38:08,240 --> 00:38:09,400
 To je isto što je...

1533
00:38:09,400 --> 00:38:10,140
 Kad gledam Depol,

1534
00:38:10,140 --> 00:38:12,460
 mi sebe zovemo da smo obite Depol,

1535
00:38:12,460 --> 00:38:16,540
 a to znači da na svakom mjestu

1536
00:38:16,540 --> 00:38:18,360
 su nam i korisnici, djelatnici i volonteri.

1537
00:38:18,360 --> 00:38:19,580
 Znači kad gledate naš uvijek,

1538
00:38:19,620 --> 00:38:21,320
 da navedim primjer kuhinje,

1539
00:38:21,320 --> 00:38:23,820
 u kuhinji je sad, evo u ovom trenutku,

1540
00:38:23,820 --> 00:38:24,780
 kad se kuha ručak,

1541
00:38:24,780 --> 00:38:26,420
 imate volontera sigurno,

1542
00:38:26,420 --> 00:38:28,460
 imate osobe koji su u probaci,

1543
00:38:28,460 --> 00:38:30,760
 imate naše korisnike,

1544
00:38:30,760 --> 00:38:33,280
 koji su se uključili u neke pomoćne poslovi,

1545
00:38:33,280 --> 00:38:34,980
 imate djelatnike, u ih smo svi.

1546
00:38:34,980 --> 00:38:36,340
 Tako da što god radimo,

1547
00:38:36,340 --> 00:38:38,020
 uvijek je ta jedna dinamika

1548
00:38:38,020 --> 00:38:39,300
 koja je na koncu ljekovita,

1549
00:38:39,300 --> 00:38:41,420
 jer jedne druge liječimo,

1550
00:38:41,420 --> 00:38:43,720
 to ne ide pomoć uvijek od mene

1551
00:38:43,720 --> 00:38:45,600
 prema čovjeku koji je kao slabiji,

1552
00:38:45,600 --> 00:38:46,920
 znači koji je u potribi.

1553
00:38:47,280 --> 00:38:48,860
 Ali pomoć je uvijek uzajamna

1554
00:38:48,860 --> 00:38:50,300
 i mislim da to je ta jedna dinamika

1555
00:38:50,300 --> 00:38:54,920
 međusobne promjene na dobro,

1556
00:38:54,920 --> 00:38:56,740
 to je nešto što je stvarno nešto

1557
00:38:56,740 --> 00:38:57,740
 što je jako, jako važno

1558
00:38:57,740 --> 00:38:59,060
 i nama je to, mislim da je to nešto

1559
00:38:59,060 --> 00:39:00,340
 što je naša osobitost,

1560
00:39:00,340 --> 00:39:01,440
 odnosno karakteristika.

1561
00:39:01,440 --> 00:39:02,840
 Imate i vrti, o tako?

1562
00:39:03,020 --> 00:39:05,480
 To su programe društveno poduzetništvo,

1563
00:39:05,480 --> 00:39:06,340
 znači to, kada kažem,

1564
00:39:06,340 --> 00:39:08,100
 to imamo vrt beskućnika

1565
00:39:08,100 --> 00:39:09,460
 koji je rasadnik,

1566
00:39:09,460 --> 00:39:10,380
 gdje imamo, proizvodimo,

1567
00:39:10,380 --> 00:39:12,860
 uzgajamo sadnice različite obilja,

1568
00:39:12,860 --> 00:39:14,680
 gnojeva različita,

1569
00:39:14,680 --> 00:39:16,420
 to su ekološka gnojeva,

1570
00:39:16,420 --> 00:39:18,120
 glisnjak, tako to je baš,

1571
00:39:18,120 --> 00:39:19,280
 ne razumijem se puno to,

1572
00:39:19,280 --> 00:39:20,660
 ali uvijek znam to što je.

1573
00:39:20,660 --> 00:39:23,980
 Imavo i naš pogon,

1574
00:39:23,980 --> 00:39:25,200
 zovemo ga kruhsatog vinka,

1575
00:39:25,200 --> 00:39:26,220
 proizvodni pogon,

1576
00:39:26,220 --> 00:39:28,600
 gdje se proizvodi različite kolači,

1577
00:39:29,480 --> 00:39:30,500
 onda krutoni,

1578
00:39:30,500 --> 00:39:32,300
 to su one prebećene kockice kruha,

1579
00:39:32,300 --> 00:39:33,820
 dehidrati,

1580
00:39:33,820 --> 00:39:35,860
 tako da to je jedan baš izdvojeni pogon.

1581
00:39:35,860 --> 00:39:37,300
 To prodajete te proizvode?

1582
00:39:37,300 --> 00:39:39,180
 Pa prodajemo, da, tako je prodajemo zaista.

1583
00:39:39,180 --> 00:39:40,140
 I gdje ih ljubi mogu nabaviti?

1584
00:39:40,140 --> 00:39:41,580
 Pa mogu nabaviti,

1585
00:39:41,580 --> 00:39:43,260
 imamo svake nedjelje,

1586
00:39:43,260 --> 00:39:44,620
 imamo, znači, na župama,

1587
00:39:44,620 --> 00:39:46,740
 riješkim župama i čak istra i lika,

1588
00:39:46,740 --> 00:39:47,960
 nekako smo počeli se širiti,

1589
00:39:47,960 --> 00:39:49,000
 to su nedeljne prodeje,

1590
00:39:49,000 --> 00:39:50,080
 a isto tako,

1591
00:39:50,080 --> 00:39:52,580
 ako neko želi naručiti kolača

1592
00:39:52,580 --> 00:39:53,300
 ili bilo što drugo,

1593
00:39:53,300 --> 00:39:54,140
 javi nam se telefon,

1594
00:39:54,260 --> 00:39:55,400
 nekako to izdefiniramo,

1595
00:39:55,400 --> 00:39:56,940
 pa zaista može se i naručivati

1596
00:39:56,940 --> 00:39:58,160
 preko naše stranice,

1597
00:39:58,160 --> 00:39:59,620
 naše kontakta i tako da.

1598
00:39:59,620 --> 00:40:00,980
 I isto tako, da,

1599
00:40:00,980 --> 00:40:01,940
 imamo neke suradnike

1600
00:40:01,940 --> 00:40:02,700
 koje se nalaze,

1601
00:40:02,700 --> 00:40:04,380
 čak i u Zagrebu,

1602
00:40:04,380 --> 00:40:07,480
 suradničke koje naše proizvode

1603
00:40:07,480 --> 00:40:08,300
 žele distribuirati,

1604
00:40:08,300 --> 00:40:09,300
 tako da na nekim mjestima

1605
00:40:09,300 --> 00:40:10,160
 se može i naći.

1606
00:40:10,160 --> 00:40:11,240
 To sam zapravo je reći,

1607
00:40:11,240 --> 00:40:12,600
 vi ste i voditeljica kuća u toči.

1608
00:40:12,600 --> 00:40:13,340
 Jesam, jesam.

1609
00:40:13,340 --> 00:40:15,420
 Zanimljivo, zanimljivo.

1610
00:40:15,420 --> 00:40:16,660
 A ovo sam mi se postavljeno,

1611
00:40:16,660 --> 00:40:18,580
 zapravo imam dva pitanja.

1612
00:40:18,580 --> 00:40:20,020
 Jedno je,

1613
00:40:21,360 --> 00:40:22,980
 jasno se znao susret s time

1614
00:40:22,980 --> 00:40:25,260
 i u svom osobnom životu

1615
00:40:25,260 --> 00:40:26,720
 i u životu drugih ljudi,

1616
00:40:26,720 --> 00:40:29,180
 a i slušajući jednostavno,

1617
00:40:29,180 --> 00:40:32,700
 čitajući o stvarnostima u crkvi,

1618
00:40:32,700 --> 00:40:34,740
 slušajući ljude kako govore

1619
00:40:34,740 --> 00:40:36,240
 o nekakvim drugim primjerima

1620
00:40:36,240 --> 00:40:37,140
 i o svojim životima,

1621
00:40:37,140 --> 00:40:39,980
 na kraju kraja i gledajući svijet

1622
00:40:39,980 --> 00:40:41,040
 i crkvu kako se ponaša,

1623
00:40:41,040 --> 00:40:42,020
 pogotovo na zapadu,

1624
00:40:42,020 --> 00:40:44,540
 zna se dogodi taj napasnost

1625
00:40:44,540 --> 00:40:47,620
 da zbog pojačanog aktivizma

1626
00:40:47,620 --> 00:40:49,380
 zapustimo ono duhovno.

1627
00:40:50,000 --> 00:40:52,200
 Da li se vi susrećate s tomu pasnošću

1628
00:40:52,200 --> 00:40:54,120
 i kako se nosite

1629
00:40:54,120 --> 00:40:55,740
 sa tim izazovima pomiriti

1630
00:40:55,740 --> 00:40:58,300
 akciju i kontemplaciju?

1631
00:40:58,300 --> 00:41:01,840
 Pa, uvezi ovog pitanja,

1632
00:41:01,840 --> 00:41:02,560
 mislim da je,

1633
00:41:02,560 --> 00:41:05,600
 volim isticati suradnju,

1634
00:41:05,600 --> 00:41:06,600
 našu suradnju,

1635
00:41:06,600 --> 00:41:07,720
 Depol Hrvatske,

1636
00:41:07,720 --> 00:41:09,440
 či Vinkovske organizacije,

1637
00:41:09,440 --> 00:41:11,860
 sa zajednicom Monitva i Riječi

1638
00:41:11,860 --> 00:41:13,160
 i Centrum za hagioterapiju.

1639
00:41:13,160 --> 00:41:15,040
 i to je ta jedna naša,

1640
00:41:15,040 --> 00:41:16,220
 kao dva krila,

1641
00:41:16,220 --> 00:41:17,040
 reklo bi se, znate,

1642
00:41:17,040 --> 00:41:18,000
 koje,

1643
00:41:18,000 --> 00:41:21,740
 iz te suradnje naše,

1644
00:41:21,740 --> 00:41:24,260
 jednostavno proizlazi

1645
00:41:24,260 --> 00:41:25,560
 iz rada,

1646
00:41:25,560 --> 00:41:26,920
 individualnog rada

1647
00:41:26,920 --> 00:41:28,200
 s korisnicima,

1648
00:41:28,200 --> 00:41:29,220
 s djelatnicima,

1649
00:41:29,220 --> 00:41:30,980
 s volonterima,

1650
00:41:30,980 --> 00:41:33,060
 proizlazi to

1651
00:41:33,060 --> 00:41:33,960
 da smo se jednostavno,

1652
00:41:33,960 --> 00:41:35,480
 sustavno smo,

1653
00:41:35,480 --> 00:41:36,600
 odlučili smo se

1654
00:41:36,600 --> 00:41:38,020
 usmjeravati na bitno.

1655
00:41:38,020 --> 00:41:40,580
 Odlučili smo se usmjeravati na bitno.

1656
00:41:40,660 --> 00:41:43,920
 to znači ne zapostavljati svoje temelje.

1657
00:41:43,920 --> 00:41:46,420
 Ne ići prema,

1658
00:41:46,420 --> 00:41:47,100
 evo što ste rekli,

1659
00:41:47,100 --> 00:41:48,480
 pretiranom aktivizmu

1660
00:41:48,480 --> 00:41:51,400
 i ne se zavaravati time.

1661
00:41:51,400 --> 00:41:52,820
 Tako da,

1662
00:41:52,820 --> 00:41:55,260
 ti programe koje mi provodimo

1663
00:41:55,260 --> 00:41:56,540
 su biti

1664
00:41:56,540 --> 00:41:59,200
 vezani i uz

1665
00:41:59,200 --> 00:42:00,940
 rad sa djelatnicima,

1666
00:42:00,940 --> 00:42:02,540
 rekla sam,

1667
00:42:02,540 --> 00:42:03,800
 individualni ili grupni,

1668
00:42:03,800 --> 00:42:05,240
 koji jednostavno

1669
00:42:05,240 --> 00:42:06,520
 dovodi do toga

1670
00:42:06,520 --> 00:42:06,980
 da smo,

1671
00:42:06,980 --> 00:42:07,620
 da jednostavno

1672
00:42:07,620 --> 00:42:08,480
 izgrađujemo

1673
00:42:08,480 --> 00:42:09,740
 tu našu obitelj,

1674
00:42:09,740 --> 00:42:10,680
 tu našu zajednicu,

1675
00:42:10,680 --> 00:42:11,220
 da jednostavno

1676
00:42:11,220 --> 00:42:13,240
 nismo nikakva tvrtka,

1677
00:42:13,240 --> 00:42:13,840
 niti smo

1678
00:42:13,840 --> 00:42:15,820
 samo neutralne osobe

1679
00:42:15,820 --> 00:42:17,820
 koje su se na jednom mjestu našle,

1680
00:42:17,820 --> 00:42:19,060
 nego osobe

1681
00:42:19,060 --> 00:42:20,280
 koje su se odlučile

1682
00:42:20,280 --> 00:42:22,180
 započeti

1683
00:42:22,180 --> 00:42:23,800
 i nastaviti

1684
00:42:23,800 --> 00:42:24,420
 tim putem

1685
00:42:24,420 --> 00:42:25,300
 osobnog rasta,

1686
00:42:25,300 --> 00:42:26,500
 odnosno ucijepljivanja

1687
00:42:26,500 --> 00:42:27,240
 u svoj temelj,

1688
00:42:27,240 --> 00:42:28,380
 to je stvoritelj Isus

1689
00:42:28,380 --> 00:42:30,140
 i iz toga djelovati.

1690
00:42:30,140 --> 00:42:31,880
 To sad,

1691
00:42:31,880 --> 00:42:32,740
 kad govorim si,

1692
00:42:33,480 --> 00:42:35,800
 možda zvuči kao da je neko savršenstvo,

1693
00:42:35,800 --> 00:42:36,760
 ali to je jedan put

1694
00:42:36,760 --> 00:42:37,660
 koji smo zaista

1695
00:42:37,660 --> 00:42:39,160
 i koji vidimo da ima

1696
00:42:39,160 --> 00:42:40,500
 i takako velike plodove.

1697
00:42:40,500 --> 00:42:41,120
 Znači,

1698
00:42:41,120 --> 00:42:42,700
 otkriti ko si kao čovjek,

1699
00:42:42,700 --> 00:42:44,920
 otkriti svoj identitet

1700
00:42:44,920 --> 00:42:46,520
 kao Isusova,

1701
00:42:46,520 --> 00:42:47,240
 znači vjernika,

1702
00:42:47,240 --> 00:42:47,960
 kao katolika,

1703
00:42:47,960 --> 00:42:48,600
 kršćanina,

1704
00:42:48,600 --> 00:42:50,300
 to je nešto što nam svima daje,

1705
00:42:50,300 --> 00:42:50,700
 evo,

1706
00:42:50,700 --> 00:42:52,020
 tu jednu dobru mjeru,

1707
00:42:52,020 --> 00:42:52,640
 ja vjerujem,

1708
00:42:52,640 --> 00:42:54,660
 odnosno,

1709
00:42:54,660 --> 00:42:55,760
 usmjerava nas

1710
00:42:55,760 --> 00:42:57,040
 kad god smo negdje

1711
00:42:57,040 --> 00:42:57,860
 izvan toga.

1712
00:42:58,800 --> 00:43:00,140
 Tako da mislim da je to nešto

1713
00:43:00,140 --> 00:43:01,280
 što nam je jako,

1714
00:43:01,280 --> 00:43:03,580
 za nas je to dosta važno,

1715
00:43:03,580 --> 00:43:04,020
 ne dosta,

1716
00:43:04,020 --> 00:43:05,200
 nego sigurno temeljno,

1717
00:43:05,200 --> 00:43:06,920
 ulagati u svoje temelje.

1718
00:43:06,920 --> 00:43:07,480
 A i sad,

1719
00:43:07,480 --> 00:43:09,000
 nije samo to,

1720
00:43:09,000 --> 00:43:09,980
 nego ulagati u to,

1721
00:43:09,980 --> 00:43:10,760
 u svoj identitet,

1722
00:43:10,760 --> 00:43:12,620
 a naš identitet je

1723
00:43:12,620 --> 00:43:13,920
 vinkovski identitet

1724
00:43:13,920 --> 00:43:14,480
 i baš smo,

1725
00:43:14,480 --> 00:43:14,940
 evo,

1726
00:43:14,940 --> 00:43:15,880
 kad smo se prošli,

1727
00:43:15,880 --> 00:43:17,280
 tijena smo imali jedan sastanak naš

1728
00:43:17,280 --> 00:43:17,840
 i baš smo rekli

1729
00:43:17,840 --> 00:43:18,980
 sljedeća godina nam je

1730
00:43:18,980 --> 00:43:20,100
 desetljeće

1731
00:43:20,100 --> 00:43:23,800
 i kao neke jubilejske godine,

1732
00:43:23,800 --> 00:43:24,760
 ako to nije jubilej,

1733
00:43:24,760 --> 00:43:26,440
 to je jednostavno deset godina

1734
00:43:26,440 --> 00:43:29,660
 da postojimo kao jedna nova organizacija,

1735
00:43:29,660 --> 00:43:30,260
 kao jedna nova,

1736
00:43:30,260 --> 00:43:30,640
 evo,

1737
00:43:30,640 --> 00:43:32,380
 kao obitelj.

1738
00:43:32,380 --> 00:43:34,720
 I da ta godina nije nam dana

1739
00:43:34,720 --> 00:43:36,720
 da sad još povećamo usluge,

1740
00:43:36,720 --> 00:43:37,600
 povećamo nešto,

1741
00:43:37,600 --> 00:43:39,340
 nego da jednostavno uđemo još više

1742
00:43:39,340 --> 00:43:40,600
 u taj svoj identitet,

1743
00:43:40,600 --> 00:43:41,040
 u mir.

1744
00:43:41,040 --> 00:43:41,960
 Evo, jednostavno,

1745
00:43:41,960 --> 00:43:42,180
 znate,

1746
00:43:42,180 --> 00:43:42,960
 kao kad zemlju,

1747
00:43:42,960 --> 00:43:44,300
 kad sad kako u ulici

1748
00:43:44,300 --> 00:43:44,980
 radim sa zemljama,

1749
00:43:44,980 --> 00:43:46,080
 vidim što to znači

1750
00:43:46,080 --> 00:43:47,080
 horati zemlju,

1751
00:43:47,080 --> 00:43:47,840
 pustiti zemlju

1752
00:43:47,840 --> 00:43:48,560
 da se odmori,

1753
00:43:48,560 --> 00:43:51,260
 dati dobre sastojke,

1754
00:43:51,260 --> 00:43:52,120
 dati dobro sjeme,

1755
00:43:52,120 --> 00:43:52,540
 prikladno,

1756
00:43:52,580 --> 00:43:53,440
 tako da sad naša godina,

1757
00:43:53,440 --> 00:43:54,380
 baš još se radujem,

1758
00:43:54,380 --> 00:43:55,300
 imat čemu.

1759
00:43:55,300 --> 00:43:56,480
 U smislu,

1760
00:43:56,480 --> 00:43:57,140
 ovom biblijsko,

1761
00:43:57,140 --> 00:43:58,300
 kao koje što je bilo zapovjećeno,

1762
00:43:58,300 --> 00:44:00,480
 da ljima dostave zemlju,

1763
00:44:00,480 --> 00:44:00,920
 da osvrljama.

1764
00:44:00,920 --> 00:44:01,320
 Ostavi,

1765
00:44:01,320 --> 00:44:02,060
 neka miruje.

1766
00:44:02,060 --> 00:44:03,860
 Zanimljiva percepcija,

1767
00:44:03,860 --> 00:44:04,640
 da ljudi baš rekli,

1768
00:44:04,640 --> 00:44:04,940
 ono,

1769
00:44:04,940 --> 00:44:05,640
 sad obljenica,

1770
00:44:05,640 --> 00:44:07,080
 sad ćemo na taj nekak projekti.

1771
00:44:07,080 --> 00:44:07,460
 Sad ćemo mi sadržaj,

1772
00:44:07,460 --> 00:44:08,600
 ajme projekti.

1773
00:44:08,600 --> 00:44:09,640
 Sigurno će i biti,

1774
00:44:09,640 --> 00:44:11,380
 ali bit će nešto

1775
00:44:11,380 --> 00:44:13,120
 što će nas dovesti

1776
00:44:13,120 --> 00:44:13,900
 u bitim.

1777
00:44:13,900 --> 00:44:16,540
 Biće nešto što nam neće biti na štetu.

1778
00:44:16,540 --> 00:44:18,760
 Što će nas vratiti na izvorima.

1779
00:44:18,760 --> 00:44:18,980
 Evo,

1780
00:44:18,980 --> 00:44:20,680
 što se vraćam opet na početka,

1781
00:44:20,680 --> 00:44:21,440
 što ti najbitnije?

1782
00:44:21,440 --> 00:44:22,140
 Pa taj izvor.

1783
00:44:22,140 --> 00:44:25,460
 Ja sam vidjela neko koje je na izvoru

1784
00:44:25,460 --> 00:44:26,600
 i to mi je privuklo.

1785
00:44:26,600 --> 00:44:27,660
 E tako,

1786
00:44:27,660 --> 00:44:28,180
 ista stvar.

1787
00:44:28,180 --> 00:44:30,380
 Spomenuli ste hagioterapiju

1788
00:44:30,380 --> 00:44:31,540
 i imate,

1789
00:44:31,540 --> 00:44:31,880
 znači,

1790
00:44:31,880 --> 00:44:32,900
